==English==
===Alternative forms===
* {{l|en|yester-year}}
===Etymology===
Compound of {{prefix|en|yester|year}}. {{coin|en|nobycat=1|Dante Gabriel Rossetti|in=1869}} in his translation "Ballad Of Dead Ladies", to translate {{noncog|frm|antan||last year}} (in Ballad 1 of {{w|François Villon}}'s ''Testament'').
